;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             ;
; Reduce the delay of 'Long Paths' in the chain                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               ;
;   or insert more pipeline stages for 'Long Paths' in the chain                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              ;
;   or remove retiming restrictions                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           ;
;    Refer to <a href='https://docs.altera.com/r/docs/683353/25.1.1/hyperflex-architecture-high-performance-design-handbook/insufficient-registers'>Insufficient Registers</a> in the <i>Altera Hyperflex Architecture High-Performance Design Handbook</i> for more information.                             ;
